00Z","msg":"聽日準時返工"},{"pid":"6b36820c738b11abb63b4cff8c5510ea3ddc890a","tid":144084,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T07:51:39.000Z","msg":"最壞情況：南斯拉夫<br />\n最好情況：俄羅斯"},{"pid":"94e18c7b933f1bb6f5063f6378abc31b899c18b8","tid":144084,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:09:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最壞情況：南斯拉夫<br />\n最好情況：俄羅斯</blockquote><br />\n唔可以咁比<br />\n因為俄羅斯都係蘇聯入面一個加盟國only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90699bcb65db37977c75f1e1124aa05b23638a55","tid":144084,"uid":4326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:10:12.000Z","msg":"香港應該直接比美帝食左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2dac62e0776ae3e4c54b2a1da940043c5334f5","tid":144084,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:13:33.000Z","msg":"廣東自成一國"},{"pid":"7c56a5136dbf36f88a45cfa627bb2b21ee68a881","tid":144084,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:21:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廣州惠州軍區照樣食左香港佢<br />\n港獨等下世啦</blockquote><br />\n駐港解放軍其實屬邊個軍區管？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3b7e0af8a72168db764cb56ceee76c2a28ed37","tid":144084,"uid":14190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:25:54.000Z","msg":"倒台後會有地下黨員再上台<br />\n名就唔同但底𥚃都係共產黨"},{"pid":"a276903b001ee8073df05447c55cf97785e9fa11","tid":144084,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:03:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最壞情況：南斯拉夫<br />\n最好情況：俄羅斯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我反而覺得中國會變成敘利亞<br />\n<br />\n即係首先有 革命軍起義........然後與中共開戰<br />\n跟住其他各地都有 恐怖組織/民兵 出現.........新疆 有類似ISIS既伊斯蘭叛軍出現等等<br />\n<br />\n中共就好似敘利亞政府咁, 唔會倒台<br />\n但領土只剩下 1/3地方.........主要是 北方地區<br />\n<br />\n中國革命軍就好似 敘利亞自由軍/反對派 咁.........主要控制南方地區<br />\n<br />\n然後西部地區, 就由各種各樣既恐怖組織/民兵控制<br />\n新疆地區就由 伊斯蘭叛軍控制<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住就日日打內戰<br />\n敘利亞都打左七年咁耐, 我諗中國至少可以打十年以上<br />\n<br />\n然後美俄日都一定搵機會加入<br />\n美國支持 革命軍<br />\n俄佬支持 只剩下北方的 中共<br />\n日本支持 東部沿海地區某D 民兵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港 有可能係美國保護下, 變成中立地區<br />\n唔會建國, 但都唔會參戰......"},{"pid":"4e1ac69442744737eec1a95bc5963413c44931a3","tid":144084,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:06:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最壞情況：南斯拉夫<br />\n最好情況：俄羅斯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我反而覺得中國會變成敘利亞<br />\n<br />\n即係首先有 革命軍起義........然後與中共開戰<br />\n跟住其他各地都有 恐怖組織/民兵 出現.........新疆 有類似ISIS既伊斯蘭叛軍出現等等<br />\n<br />\n中共就好似敘利亞政府咁, 唔會倒台<br />\n但領土只剩下 1/3地方.........主要是 北方地區<br />\n<br />\n中國革命軍就好似 敘利亞自由軍/反對派 咁.........主要控制南方地區<br />\n<br />\n然後西部地區, 就由各種各樣既恐怖組織/民兵控制<br />\n新疆地區就由 伊斯蘭叛軍控制<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住就日日打內戰<br />\n敘利亞都打左七年咁耐, 我諗中國至少可以打十年以上<br />\n<br />\n然後美俄日都一定搵機會加入<br />\n美國支持 革命軍<br />\n俄佬支持 只剩下北方的 中共<br />\n日本支持 東部沿海地區某D 民兵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港 有可能係美國保護下, 變成中立地區<br />\n唔會建國, 但都唔會參戰......</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n敘利亞內戰版圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/68/Syrian_Civil_War_map.svg/983px-Syrian_Civil_War_map.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F6%2F68%2FSyrian_Civil_War_map.svg%2F983px-Syrian_Civil_War_map.svg.png&h=7293609c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d4373c9728428023dd56127a1e9000c9c8ef48f","tid":144084,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:09:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n敘利亞內戰版圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/68/Syrian_Civil_War_map.svg/983px-Syrian_Civil_War_map.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F6%2F68%2FSyrian_Civil_War_map.svg%2F983px-Syrian_Civil_War_map.svg.png&h=7293609c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n紅色 = 敘利亞政府<br />\n只剩下中央地區.........<br />\n<br />\n綠色 = 自由軍/反對派/革命軍<br />\n<br />\n白色 = 努斯拉陣線<br />\n<br />\n黃色 = 庫爾德軍隊<br />\n<br />\n黑色 = ISIS<br />\n<br />\n將來中國應該差唔多<br />\n可能會更加勢力"},{"pid":"073716fa2fbd3ec23bce8335da67426d614e3f3d","tid":144084,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:09:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n敘利亞內戰版圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/68/Syrian_Civil_War_map.svg/983px-Syrian_Civil_War_map.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F6%2F68%2FSyrian_Civil_War_map.svg%2F983px-Syrian_Civil_War_map.svg.png&h=7293609c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n紅色 = 敘利亞政府<br />\n只剩下中央地區.........<br />\n<br />\n綠色 = 自由軍/反對派/革命軍<br />\n<br />\n白色 = 努斯拉陣線<br />\n<br />\n黃色 = 庫爾德軍隊<br />\n<br />\n黑色 = ISIS<br />\n<br />\n將來中國應該差唔多<br />\n可能會更多勢力</blockquote>"},{"pid":"6a0455efecfce8c9b07df3356c1f140d645491d3","tid":144084,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:10:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>廣州惠州軍區照樣食左香港佢<br />\n港獨等下世啦</blockquote><br />\n駐港解放軍其實屬邊個軍區管？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n軍區已經取消左,  家陣是南部戰區"},{"pid":"c9dd2173172e76d78e8282aa1202354ccef8794d","tid":144084,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:12:51.000Z","msg":"太空泛了<br />\n<br />\n在甚麼環境下和如何發生?明天的話即是政變成功。那新的掌權者能掌握整個江山?有派系/軍隊出兵勤王?太broad了"},{"pid":"aab541ff742c4342a6cc52b39c1e28a055f6fc82","tid":144084,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:13:33.000Z","msg":"其實睇番中國歷史<br />\n<br />\n中國政權, 唔會好似蘇聯咁, 和平倒台<br />\n<br />\n一係被起義軍推翻<br />\n一係被人發動政變推翻<br />\n一係被外國軍隊入侵消滅<br />\n總之都係要打仗<br />\n<br />\n而且中國政權倒台之後, 一般都會打內戰<br />\n最後再統一番"},{"pid":"9d3e037023d6609e526628dab7c6